## Write a program to convert weeks to hours

1 week = 7 days = 168 hours

```
Input  : 5
Output : 840
```

---

<CodeBlock slug="convert-weeks-to-hours" >

```c
#include <stdio.h>

void main()
{
    int num;

    printf("Enter number of weeks : ");
    scanf("%d", &num);

    int total_hours;

    total_hours = num * 168;

    printf("\nTotal hours is  : %d\n", total_hours);
}
```

